(144, 'What parents should know about the VR gear kids want', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_technology/~3/y68-a5NpJLA/index.html', 'Thinking about treating your family to a little virtual reality this holiday? Have no idea where to start? Don\'t worry. From Google\'s inexpensive Cardboard VR viewer to Sony\'s new PlayStation VR, this guide will help you figure out what makes sense for your family\'s interests, needs and budget.', 'NO_IMAGE', 'Thu, 17 Nov 2016 11:12:43 EST', 'CNN', 'technology'),
