(662, 'Canadian schools adapt to children with ADHD', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190506-focus-canada-adhd-quebec-teaching-schools-universities-children-students', 'The Canadian province of Quebec has decided to adapt its education system to the increasing number of children diagnosed with Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD). Doctors in Canada recognise ADHD as a neurological disorder and treat it with medication, as well as advising to cut sugary foods and screen time. Our correspondents report on how schools and universities in Quebec are helping to support those affected by ADHD.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/edition/fr_nw_pkg_focus_0506_canada_trouble_deficit_attention.jpg', 'Mon, 06 May 2019 13:26:04 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
(663, 'Maduro rallies troops against US after opposition asks army to join protests', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190505-maduro-rallies-troops-opposition-guaido-asks-military-join-anti-regime-protests', 'Venezuelan President Nicolas Maduro urged the army on Saturday to be ready for a possible US military intervention against his regime, days after opposition leader Juan Guaido appealed to troops to join the rebellion against Maduro.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/article/image/venezuela_29.jpg', 'Sun, 05 May 2019 07:32:27 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
(664, 'No fatalities as Boeing 737 slides off runway into Florida river', 'https://www.france24.com/en/http/bartfrance24com/en/20190504-usa-boeing-737-no-fatalities-plane-jacksonville-florida-river-land', 'A Boeing jetliner with 143 people aboard from the US outpost at Guantanamo Bay, Cuba, slid off a runway Friday into a shallow river in Jacksonville, Florida, while attempting to land in a thunderstorm.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/article/image/boeing_jacksonville.jpg', 'Sat, 04 May 2019 09:47:29 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
(665, 'Will the Venezuelan army remain loyal to Maduro?', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190503-inside-americas-venezuela-maduro-guaido-army-canada-flooding-baltimore-violence-music', 'Venezuela was rocked by new protests this week as opposition leader Juan Guaido declared the final phase of what he\'s dubbed \"Operation Freedom\". He\'s got the backing of some 50 countries around the world in his quest to take power away from President Nicolas Maduro. But the key to the power struggle lies with Venezuela\'s powerful army. The military has always played an important role in the political life of the country, taking part in coups that have both toppled and restored power. ', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/edition/xx_mg_freeze_venezuela_army.jpg', 'Fri, 03 May 2019 10:47:42 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
(666, 'Venezuela\'s Maduro appears with military leaders to denounce \'coup plotters\'', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190503-venezuela-maduro-appears-with-military-leaders-denounce-coup-guaido', 'Venezuelan President Nicolas Maduro on Thursday called on the armed forces to oppose \"any coup plotter\" after a military uprising in support of opposition leader Juan Guaido fizzled out, and subsequent street clashes left four protesters dead.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/article/image/020519_maduro.jpg', 'Thu, 02 May 2019 23:51:53 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
(667, 'US Attorney Barr refuses to testify before House over Mueller report', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190502-barr-denies-whitewash-mueller-report-before-senate-trump', 'US Attorney General Bill Barr rejected allegations in a Senate hearing Wednesday that he had whitewashed the Mueller Russian interference report to protect Donald Trump, but refused to appear before the House for questioning on Thursday.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/article/image/063_1140512409.jpg', 'Wed, 01 May 2019 22:42:21 GMT', 'France 24', 'americas'),
