(762, 'Arundhati Roy speaks to FRANCE 24 about India\'s election', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190502-india-votes-arundhati-roy-modi-bjp-rss-economic-record-congress-party-gandhi-polls', 'In this edition of India Votes we speak to Man Booker Prize-winning author and activist Arundhati Roy. She believes India\'s Prime Minister Narendra Modi won\'t be returning for a second term, given that \"he shot off the tyres of an economy that was on the move\". ', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/edition/india_votes_2may.jpg', 'Thu, 02 May 2019 16:03:18 GMT', 'France 24', 'asia'),
(763, 'China ranks \'good\' and \'bad\' citizens with \'social credit\' system ', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190501-focus-china-social-credit-system-mass-surveillance-citizens-ranking-behaviour-criticism', 'In China, where millions of people have their faces scanned on a daily basis, authorities are developing a so-called \"social credit\" system. Citizensâ€™ behavior is monitored and scrutinised â€“ they are given scores and ranked according to rules set by the government. \"Model\" citizens enjoy perks such as reduced bus fares, but those with low scores lose certain rights and are blacklisted. Our colleagues from France 2 report, with FRANCE 24â€™s Emerald Maxwell.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/edition/fr_nw_pkg_focus_0501_chine_credit_social_notation_des_citoyens_ok.jpg', 'Wed, 01 May 2019 13:47:09 GMT', 'France 24', 'asia'),
(764, 'Australian scientists find antidote for deadly box jellyfish sting', 'https://www.france24.com/en/20190501-australian-scientists-find-antidote-deadly-box-jellyfish-sting', 'Australian researchers believe they have found an antidote to a sting from the world\'s most venomous creature, the much-feared box jellyfish.', 'https://scd.france24.com/en/files/imagecache/france24_ct_api_medium2/article/image/jellyfish_-_m.jpg', 'Wed, 01 May 2019 10:24:50 GMT', 'France 24', 'asia'),
(765, 'China denies having \'concentration camps,\' tells US to \'stop interfering\'', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_asia/~3/mULXcqEeEw8/index.html', 'Beijing has rejected US accusations of operating \"concentration camps\" in its Xinjiang region, with a government spokesman telling Washington Monday to \"stop interfering in Chinese domestic affairs.\"', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190502093713-china-police-xinjiang-super-169.jpg', 'Mon, 06 May 2019 23:36:43 GMT', 'CNN', 'asia'),
