(772, 'Japan\'s samurai swordsmiths cling to a centuries-old craft', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_asia/~3/CrGUl-H3Bwo/index.html', 'At Fusahiro Shimojima\'s workshop, in the industrial city of Saitama, fires rage in small pits and an earthen floor absorbs the din of hammering. The 44-year-old Japanese swordsmith pounds the nascent blade of his newest creation, sending molten sparks flying majestically into air.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/181004110429-samurai-sword-tease-1-super-169.jpg', 'Wed, 17 Oct 2018 02:25:42 GMT', 'CNN', 'asia'),
(773, 'Classic paintings with tiny manga characters', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_asia/~3/b6Ze_0zRbvQ/index.html', 'Leonardo da Vinci\'s \"Mona Lisa\" is one of the world\'s most reproduced and reinterpreted paintings -- but no one has done it quite like Japanese artist Keita Sagaki.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/180215164031-mona-lisa-closer-crop-for-card-super-169.jpg', 'Mon, 19 Feb 2018 09:10:39 GMT', 'CNN', 'asia'),
(774, 'Hidden emotions of Japanese Noh masks', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_asia/~3/zcDd8LOFae0/index.html', 'Their almond-shaped eyes stare blankly into space. The ambivalent corners of their mouths leave their moods utterly indiscernible.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/180312095405-yakan-eye-super-169.jpg', 'Mon, 15 Oct 2018 03:39:00 GMT', 'CNN', 'asia'),
(775, 'World\'s largest underwater restaurant nears completion', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_asia/~3/d4ibZk0j6vo/index.html', 'Five meters below the surface of the North Sea, near the southernmost tip of Norway, Europe\'s first underwater restaurant is nearing completion. The 110-foot long structure, an oblique concrete slab that looks like a sunken periscope, was submerged in July 2018 and work is now underway to complete the interiors, in anticipation of the public opening in spring 2019.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/180926161220-snohetta-under2016226-os-n3-super-169.jpg', 'Thu, 21 Mar 2019 13:38:49 GMT', 'CNN', 'asia'),
