(991, 'New York City now has a Wu-Tang Clan District', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/ajX09lVg99o/index.html', 'The Wu-Tang Clan will live on forever in New York City\'s streets.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190505130147-wu-tang-clan-restricted-super-169.jpg', 'Sun, 05 May 2019 18:21:30 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(992, 'SpongeBob and the 7 life lessons he taught a generation', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/eWVNnOwpSX0/index.html', 'It\'s been 20 years, and the little sponge who lives in a pineapple under the sea still resonates with people around the world.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190503220200-spongebob-squarepants-story-top-super-169.jpg', 'Sun, 05 May 2019 04:20:23 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(993, 'Andy Cohen received GLAAD\'s Vito Russo award and gave a touching speech about being gay and his son', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/_MJwyWrf76g/index.html', 'After 21-year-old Andy Cohen came out as gay during his time as a CBS intern, he never looked back.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190505232450-andy-cohen-1-super-169.jpg', 'Mon, 06 May 2019 04:24:19 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(994, 'See what\'s streaming in May', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/jirHTHoEDi8/index.html', 'Mother may I stay in and watch what\'s streaming?', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190424182701-29-whats-streaming-may-2019-super-169.jpg', 'Sun, 28 Apr 2019 15:24:08 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(995, '\'Long Shot\' unevenly blends political satire and romantic comedy', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/ORnjY9KuUqo/index.html', '\"Long Shot\" is a movie somewhat at war with itself, seeking to combine political satire with crude (in the mode of many Seth Rogen movies) romantic comedy. Both elements work in fits and starts, but they tend to offset each other, yielding a film more enjoyable for individual moments than any sort of cohesive whole.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190430082318-long-shot-theron-rogen-super-169.jpg', 'Thu, 02 May 2019 18:33:01 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(996, '\'Chernobyl\' turns the Soviet nuclear disaster into a riveting miniseries', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/NMKO1B_-SfU/index.html', 'Spare, bleak and devastating, HBO\'s \"Chernobyl\" captures a moment during the waning years of the Cold War when the Soviet Union experienced a nuclear disaster, then tried to cover up the extent of the damage.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190502074749-chernobyl-hbo-super-169.jpg', 'Sun, 05 May 2019 15:58:47 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment'),
(997, 'Holocaust survivors and liberators look back in twin documentaries', 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/edition_entertainment/~3/LNSvBXsgVCg/index.html', 'The resurgence of white supremacism has brought a renewed urgency to Holocaust Remembrance Day, and specifically the sense that the world is gradually losing those capable of providing first-hand accounts. That\'s evident in a pair of complementary documentaries this week, looking back through the eyes of camp survivors and their liberators.', 'https://cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/190429100928-the-last-survivors-pbs-super-169.jpg', 'Tue, 30 Apr 2019 16:29:12 GMT', 'CNN', 'entertainment');
